<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
    <%- include('../../includes/head', locals) %>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" />
    
    <style>
        /* ==========================================================================
           1. CẤU HÌNH BIẾN TOÀN CỤC (GLOBAL VARIABLES) - TONE MÀU SÁNG THANH LỊCH
           ========================================================================== */
        :root { 
            /* Bảng màu chủ đạo (Color Palette) */
            --game-bg: #f4f7f6; 
            --game-primary: #e74c3c; 
            --game-primary-hover: #c0392b;
            --game-gold: #f1c40f; 
            --game-gold-hover: #f39c12;
            --game-cyan: #00cec9;
            --game-dark: #2d3436;
            --game-gray: #b2bec3;
            --game-light: #ffffff;
            
            /* Cấu hình đổ bóng (Box Shadows) */
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --shadow-md: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --shadow-lg: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
            --shadow-colored: 0 8px 20px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.2);
            
            /* Cấu hình bo góc (Border Radius) */
            --border-radius-sm: 8px;
            --border-radius-md: 15px;
            --border-radius-lg: 20px;
            --border-radius-xl: 30px;
            
            /* Cấu hình hiệu ứng chuyển động (Transitions) */
            --transition-fast: 0.2s ease-in-out;
            --transition-normal: 0.3s ease-in-out;
            --transition-slow: 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           2. THIẾT LẬP CƠ BẢN (RESET & BASE TYPOGRAPHY)
           ========================================================================== */
        body { 
            background-color: var(--game-bg); 
            font-family: 'Inter', 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        /* Áp dụng Font chữ hiển thị chuyên biệt cho các Tiêu đề và Nút bấm */
        h1, 
        h2, 
        h3, 
        h4, 
        h5, 
        h6, 
        .btn, 
        .qa-item { 
            font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', sans-serif; 
        }

        /* Ẩn thanh cuộn (Scrollbar) nhưng vẫn cho phép vuốt/scroll */
        .hide-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .hide-scrollbar {
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }

        /* Lớp Animation (AOS - Animate On Scroll) dùng cho JS bên dưới */
        .aos-init {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.6s ease-out, transform 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        .aos-animate {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           3. KHU VỰC BANNER CHÍNH TRÊN CÙNG (MAIN SLIDER)
           ========================================================================== */
        .main-banner-zone {
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 15px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .banner-slider { 
            width: 100%; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md); 
            overflow: hidden; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); 
            background: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .banner-slider img { 
            width: 100%; 
            height: auto; 
            object-fit: cover; 
            aspect-ratio: 21/9; 
            display: block;
            transition: transform var(--transition-slow);
        }

        /* Hiệu ứng zoom nhẹ bức ảnh khi slide đó đang hiện (Active) */
        .swiper-slide-active img {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

        .swiper-pagination-bullet {
            background: var(--game-light);
            opacity: 0.6;
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            transition: width var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .swiper-pagination-bullet-active {
            background: var(--game-primary);
            opacity: 1;
            width: 25px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           4. MENU TRUY CẬP NHANH (QUICK ACTIONS NAV)
           ========================================================================== */
        .qa-nav-wrapper {
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-left: 5px;
            padding-right: 5px;
        }

        .qa-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            /* Đã chuyển từ 8 xuống 7 cột do ẩn Gieo Quẻ */
            grid-template-columns: repeat(7, 1fr);
            gap: 15px; 
            text-align: center; 
        }

        .qa-item { 
            text-decoration: none; 
            color: var(--game-dark); 
            font-weight: 700; 
            font-size: 13px; 
            transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast); 
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
        }

        .qa-item:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-5px); 
            background: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .qa-item:active { 
            transform: scale(0.95); 
        }

        .qa-icon { 
            width: 60px; 
            height: 60px; 
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: auto;
            border-radius: 20px; 
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            font-size: 26px; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: border-radius var(--transition-normal);
        }

        .qa-item:hover .qa-icon {
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Hiệu ứng tia sáng lướt qua Icon (Shine Effect) */
        .qa-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%; 
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%; 
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 100%);
            transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(-100%);
            animation: shineIcon 3s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes shineIcon {
            0% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(-100%); }
            20% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(100%); }
            100% { transform: rotate(45deg) translateY(100%); }
        }

        /* Cấu hình màu nền Gradient cho từng nút truy cập nhanh */
        .qa-icon.uytin { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894, #00cec9); }
        .qa-icon.tuimu { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1c40f, #e67e22); color: #ffffff;}
        .qa-icon.thueacc { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b59b6, #8e44ad); }
        .qa-icon.san1d { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00cec9, #00b894); }
        .qa-icon.minigame { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b); }
        .qa-icon.chungsuc { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9); }
        .qa-icon.caythue { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd79a8, #e84393); }

        /* ==========================================================================
           5. TIÊU ĐỀ CÁC KHU VỰC (SECTION HEADERS)
           ========================================================================== */
        .section-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e1e8ed;
            position: relative;
        }

        .section-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -2px;
            left: 0;
            width: 80px;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--game-primary);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--game-dark);
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .section-title i {
            color: var(--game-primary);
        }

        .btn-view-all {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #3498db;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            transition: color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .btn-view-all:hover {
            color: var(--game-primary);
            transform: translateX(3px);
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           6. LOBBY SỰ KIỆN NỔI BẬT
           ========================================================================== */
        .hot-events-wrapper {
            margin-top: 40px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        /* 1. Mega Banner: Check Uy Tín (Ưu tiên số 1) */
        .mega-promo-banner.trust {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00b894, #00cec9);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 184, 148, 0.3);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .mega-promo-banner.trust::before {
            content: '\f328';
            font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
            font-weight: 900;
            position: absolute;
            top: -20px;
            right: -20px;
            font-size: 150px;
            opacity: 0.15;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }

        /* 2. Mega Banner: TÚI MÙ (Thay thế Gieo Quẻ) */
        .mega-promo-banner.tuimu {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #d35400);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(211, 84, 0, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #f1c40f;
        }

        .mega-promo-banner.tuimu::before {
            content: '\f06b'; /* Icon Hộp Quà */
            font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
            font-weight: 900;
            position: absolute;
            top: -30px;
            left: -20px;
            font-size: 160px;
            opacity: 0.1;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
        }

        /* Typography cho Mega Banner */
        .mp-title {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            margin-left: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            font-family: 'Be Vietnam Pro', serif;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .mega-promo-banner.trust .mp-title { color: #ffffff; }
        .mega-promo-banner.tuimu .mp-title { color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }

        .mp-desc {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: 0;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            margin-left: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            max-width: 650px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .btn-play-mega {
            font-weight: 900;
            padding: 16px 45px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-xl);
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: transform var(--transition-normal), box-shadow var(--transition-normal), background var(--transition-normal);
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .btn-play-mega.trust-btn { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            color: #00b894; 
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); 
        }
        
        .btn-play-mega.tm-btn { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            color: #d35400; 
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15); 
        }

        .btn-play-mega:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-3px) scale(1.05); 
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           7. LƯỚI DỊCH VỤ (TÚI MÙ, THUÊ ACC, SĂN 1Đ, MINIGAME, CHUNG SỨC, CÀY THUÊ)
           ========================================================================== */
        .services-scroll-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .svc-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
            padding: 25px 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            text-decoration: none;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
            transition: transform var(--transition-normal), box-shadow var(--transition-normal);
        }

        .svc-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
        }

        .svc-icon-wrap {
            width: 70px;
            height: 70px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #ffffff;
            transition: transform var(--transition-fast);
        }

        .svc-card:hover .svc-icon-wrap {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
        }
        
        /* Cấu hình riêng cho từng khối dịch vụ */
        .svc-tuimu .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f1c40f, #e67e22); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(241,196,15,0.4);}
        .svc-tuimu { border-bottom: 5px solid #f1c40f; }
        
        .svc-thueacc .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b59b6, #8e44ad); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(155,89,182,0.4);}
        .svc-thueacc { border-bottom: 5px solid #9b59b6; }

        .svc-san1d .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00cec9, #00b894); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,206,201,0.4);}
        .svc-san1d { border-bottom: 5px solid #00cec9; }

        .svc-minigame .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(231,76,60,0.4);}
        .svc-minigame { border-bottom: 5px solid #e74c3c; }

        .svc-chungsuc .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3498db, #2980b9); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(52,152,219,0.4);}
        .svc-chungsuc { border-bottom: 5px solid #3498db; }

        .svc-caythue .svc-icon-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fd79a8, #e84393); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(253,121,168,0.4);}
        .svc-caythue { border-bottom: 5px solid #fd79a8; }
        
        .svc-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--game-dark);
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: 0;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            margin-left: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .svc-desc {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #636e72;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-right: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            margin-left: 0;
            flex-grow: 1;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .svc-action {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 800;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            transition: gap var(--transition-fast);
        }

        /* Phối màu cho chữ Action dựa theo Theme của thẻ */
        .svc-tuimu .svc-action { color: #d35400; }
        .svc-thueacc .svc-action { color: #8e44ad; }
        .svc-san1d .svc-action { color: #00b894; }
        .svc-minigame .svc-action { color: #c0392b; }
        .svc-chungsuc .svc-action { color: #2980b9; }
        .svc-caythue .svc-action { color: #e84393; }
        
        .svc-card:hover .svc-action { 
            gap: 10px; /* Hiệu ứng đẩy mũi tên ra xa khi hover */
        }

        /* Dấu mác HOT góc phải */
        .tag-hot-corner {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: -30px;
            background: #e74c3c;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 900;
            padding: 5px 40px;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            z-index: 5;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           8. SẢNH KHO TÀI KHOẢN (CAROUSEL VUỐT NGANG)
           ========================================================================== */
        .account-showcase-zone {
            margin-top: 50px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff, var(--game-bg));
            padding: 30px 20px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }
        
        .acc-slider-container { 
            width: 100%; 
            padding-top: 10px; 
            padding-bottom: 30px; /* Để shadow không bị cắt */
            overflow: hidden; 
        }
        
        .acc-slide-card {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            border: 1px solid #f1f2f6;
            transition: transform var(--transition-normal), box-shadow var(--transition-normal), border-color var(--transition-normal);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .acc-slide-card:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-8px); 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); 
            border-color: var(--game-primary); 
        }
        
        .acc-thumb { 
            position: relative; 
            width: 100%; 
            padding-top: 56.25%; /* Tỉ lệ 16:9 cho ảnh Acc */
            overflow: hidden; 
        }

        .acc-thumb img { 
            position: absolute; 
            top: 0; 
            left: 0; 
            width: 100%; 
            height: 100%; 
            object-fit: cover; 
            transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out; 
        }

        .acc-slide-card:hover .acc-thumb img { 
            transform: scale(1.1); 
        }

        .acc-tag-new { 
            position: absolute; 
            top: 8px; 
            left: 8px; 
            background: #e74c3c; 
            color: #ffffff; 
            font-size: 10px; 
            font-weight: 900; 
            padding: 3px 8px; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            z-index: 2; 
        }
        
        .acc-info { 
            padding: 15px; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            flex-grow: 1; 
        }

        .acc-name { 
            font-size: 14px; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            color: var(--game-dark); 
            margin-top: 0; 
            margin-bottom: 10px; 
            line-height: 1.4; 
            height: 40px; 
            overflow: hidden; 
            display: -webkit-box; 
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2; 
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical; 
        }

        .acc-ms { 
            font-size: 11px; 
            color: #7f8c8d; 
            margin-bottom: 10px; 
            padding-bottom: 10px; 
            border-bottom: 1px dashed #eeeeee; 
        }

        .acc-price-box { 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
            margin-top: auto; 
        }

        .acc-price-old { 
            font-size: 12px; 
            color: #95a5a6; 
            text-decoration: line-through; 
        }

        .acc-price-new { 
            font-size: 18px; 
            font-weight: 900; 
            color: var(--game-primary); 
        }

        .btn-view-acc { 
            display: block; 
            width: 100%; 
            text-align: center; 
            background: #f8f9fa; 
            color: var(--game-primary); 
            border: 1px solid var(--game-primary); 
            font-size: 12px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            padding: 10px 0; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            transition: background var(--transition-fast), color var(--transition-fast); 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
        }

        .btn-view-acc:hover { 
            background: var(--game-primary); 
            color: #ffffff; 
        }

        .btn-massive-store {
            display: flex; 
            align-items: center; 
            justify-content: center; 
            gap: 10px;
            width: max-content; 
            margin: 20px auto 0; 
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background: var(--game-dark); 
            color: #ffffff; 
            font-size: 14px; 
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            border-radius: 50px; 
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(45, 52, 54, 0.4); 
            transition: transform var(--transition-normal), box-shadow var(--transition-normal), background var(--transition-normal);
        }

        .btn-massive-store:hover { 
            transform: translateY(-3px); 
            background: #1a1e21; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(45, 52, 54, 0.6); 
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           9. KHU VỰC NẠP THẺ TỰ ĐỘNG
           ========================================================================== */
        .recharge-zone { 
            margin-top: 50px; 
        }

        .recharge-wrapper { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 25px; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg); 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); 
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed; 
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           10. KHU VỰC TIN TỨC & CẨM NANG
           ========================================================================== */
        .news-zone { 
            margin-top: 50px; 
            margin-bottom: 40px; 
        }

        .news-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; 
            gap: 20px; 
        }
        
        .news-hot-card { 
            display: block; 
            position: relative; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md); 
            overflow: hidden; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            height: 100%; 
            min-height: 280px; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); 
        }

        .news-hot-card img { 
            width: 100%; 
            height: 100%; 
            object-fit: cover; 
            position: absolute; 
            top: 0; 
            left: 0; 
            transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out; 
        }

        .news-hot-card:hover img { 
            transform: scale(1.05); 
        }

        .news-hot-overlay { 
            position: absolute; 
            bottom: 0; 
            left: 0; 
            width: 100%; 
            background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.9)); 
            padding: 40px 20px 20px 20px; 
            color: #ffffff; 
        }

        .news-tag-hot { 
            background: var(--game-primary); 
            font-size: 10px; 
            padding: 4px 12px; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            font-weight: 800; 
        }

        .news-hot-title { 
            font-size: 18px; 
            margin-top: 10px; 
            margin-bottom: 0; 
            line-height: 1.4; 
            text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); 
            font-weight: 800; 
        }

        .news-list-wrap { 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            gap: 15px; 
        }

        .news-mini-card { 
            display: flex; 
            gap: 15px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 12px; 
            border-radius: 12px; 
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.03); 
            border: 1px solid #f1f2f6; 
            transition: transform var(--transition-fast), border-color var(--transition-fast); 
        }

        .news-mini-card:hover { 
            border-color: var(--game-cyan); 
            transform: translateX(5px); 
        }

        .news-mini-img { 
            width: 110px; 
            height: 80px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            object-fit: cover; 
        }

        .news-mini-content { 
            flex: 1; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            justify-content: center; 
        }

        .news-mini-title { 
            font-size: 14px; 
            color: var(--game-dark); 
            margin-bottom: 8px; 
            line-height: 1.4; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            display: -webkit-box; 
            -webkit-line-clamp: 2; 
            -webkit-box-orient: vertical; 
            overflow: hidden; 
        }

        .news-mini-meta { 
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            font-size: 11px; 
            color: #95a5a6; 
            font-weight: 600; 
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           11. KHU VỰC SEO BÀI BẢN VÀ SCHEMA
           ========================================================================== */
        .seo-content { 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md); 
            margin-top: 50px; 
            font-size: 13px; 
            color: #555555; 
            line-height: 1.8; 
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); 
            border: 1px dashed #cccccc; 
        }

        .seo-content h1 { 
            font-size: 18px; 
            color: var(--game-primary); 
            margin-bottom: 12px; 
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .seo-content h2, 
        .seo-content h3 { 
            font-size: 15px; 
            color: var(--game-dark); 
            margin-top: 20px; 
            margin-bottom: 8px; 
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .seo-content p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .seo-content strong { 
            color: #d35400; 
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* ==========================================================================
           12. MEDIA QUERIES - THIẾT KẾ ĐỘC QUYỀN CHO MOBILE (BỐ CỤC 2 CỘT CHUẨN)
           ========================================================================== */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .qa-grid { 
                grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); 
                gap: 10px; 
            }
            .news-grid { 
                grid-template-columns: 1fr; 
            }
            .news-hot-card { 
                min-height: 220px; 
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            /* 1. Rút gọn Banner Chính */
            .banner-slider { 
                border-radius: 10px; 
                margin-top: 10px; 
            }
            
            /* 2. Menu Truy Cập Nhanh thành vuốt ngang */
            .qa-nav-wrapper { 
                margin: 20px -15px; 
                padding: 0 15px; 
            }
            .qa-grid { 
                display: flex; 
                overflow-x: auto; 
                scroll-snap-type: x mandatory; 
                padding-bottom: 15px; 
                gap: 5px; 
            }
            .qa-item { 
                flex: 0 0 22%; /* Hiển thị 4.5 item để user biết có thể vuốt */
                scroll-snap-align: start; 
                padding: 5px; 
            }
            .qa-icon { 
                width: 50px; 
                height: 50px; 
                font-size: 20px; 
                border-radius: 14px;
            }
            .qa-item span { 
                font-size: 11px; 
                white-space: nowrap; 
            }

            /* 3. ĐIỀU CHỈNH LƯỚI DỊCH VỤ THÀNH 2 CỘT DỌC ĐỂ CHỐNG DÀI TRANG */
            .services-scroll-container {
                display: grid !important;
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important; /* HIỂN THỊ 2 CỘT MỖI HÀNG */
                gap: 12px !important;
                margin: 0 !important;
                padding: 0 !important;
                overflow: visible !important;
            }
            
            .svc-card { 
                flex: none !important;
                padding: 15px 10px !important; 
                text-align: center !important;
                align-items: center !important;
                justify-content: center !important;
            }
            
            .svc-icon-wrap {
                width: 45px !important;
                height: 45px !important;
                font-size: 20px !important;
                margin-bottom: 10px !important;
            }

            .svc-title {
                font-size: 13px !important;
                margin-bottom: 5px !important;
            }

            .svc-desc {
                font-size: 11px !important;
                margin-bottom: 10px !important;
                display: -webkit-box;
                -webkit-line-clamp: 2; /* Chỉ hiện 2 dòng mô tả */
                -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

            .svc-action {
                font-size: 11px !important;
                flex-direction: column !important;
                gap: 3px !important;
                margin-top: auto;
            }

            .tag-hot-corner {
                top: 8px;
                right: -25px;
                padding: 3px 25px;
                font-size: 9px;
            }
            
            /* Điều chỉnh Mega Banner cho vừa Mobile */
            .mp-title { 
                font-size: 22px; 
            }
            .btn-play-mega { 
                padding: 12px 25px; 
                font-size: 14px; 
            }

            /* 4. Kho Acc Showcase tối ưu cho Mobile */
            .account-showcase-zone { 
                padding: 20px 15px; 
            }
            .btn-massive-store { 
                width: 100%; 
                justify-content: center; 
                padding: 14px 20px; 
            }

            .section-title { 
                font-size: 18px; 
            }
            .recharge-wrapper { 
                padding: 15px; 
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <%- include('../../includes/ui-common') %>
    <%- include('../../includes/header') %>
    <%- include('../../includes/mobile-nav') %>

    <main class="container">
        
        <div class="main-banner-zone aos-init">
            <div class="swiper banner-slider">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                    <% if(typeof banners !== 'undefined' && banners.length > 0) { %>
                        <% banners.forEach(b => { %>
                            <div class="swiper-slide">
                                <a href="<%= b.link %>">
                                    <img src="<%= b.image_url %>" alt="Banner Khuyến Mãi ShopLienQuan">
                                </a>
                            </div>
                        <% }) %>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="qa-nav-wrapper aos-init">
            <nav class="qa-grid hide-scrollbar" aria-label="Menu Truy Cập Nhanh">
                <a href="/check-uy-tin" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon uytin"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div><span>Uy Tín</span></a>
                <a href="/tui-mu" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon tuimu"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift"></i></div><span>Túi Mù</span></a>
                <a href="/thue-acc" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon thueacc"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div><span>Thuê Acc</span></a>
                <a href="/san-acc-1d" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon san1d"><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i></div><span>Săn Nick 1Đ</span></a>
                <a href="/minigame" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon minigame"><i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i></div><span>Vòng Quay</span></a>
                <a href="/chung-suc" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon chungsuc"><i class="fa-solid fa-people-group"></i></div><span>Chung Sức</span></a>
                <a href="/cay-thue" class="qa-item"><div class="qa-icon caythue"><i class="fa-solid fa-khanda"></i></div><span>Cày Thuê</span></a>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <section class="hot-events-wrapper">
            <div class="section-header aos-init">
                <h2 class="section-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-fire"></i> SỰ KIỆN HOT TRONG TUẦN</h2>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mega-promo-banner trust aos-init">
                <h3 class="mp-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> GIAO DỊCH UY TÍN 100%</h3>
                <p class="mp-desc">Hàng ngàn giao dịch thành công mỗi ngày. Check lịch sử nạp thẻ và mua acc minh bạch, công khai để anh em yên tâm giao dịch.</p>
                <a href="/check-uy-tin" class="btn-play-mega trust-btn">
                    XEM BẰNG CHỨNG GIAO DỊCH <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="mega-promo-banner tuimu aos-init">
                <h3 class="mp-title"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift"></i> ĐẠI TIỆC TÚI MÙ GACHA</h3>
                <p class="mp-desc">Chỉ từ 9.000đ - Mở ra Acc Liên Quân Siêu VIP. Cơ hội trúng Skin SSS, nick Thách Đấu với tỷ lệ cực cao. Xé túi thử nhân phẩm ngay!</p>
                <a href="/tui-mu" class="btn-play-mega tm-btn">
                    XÉ TÚI MÙ NGAY <i class="fa-solid fa-box-open"></i>
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="services-scroll-container hide-scrollbar aos-init">
                
                <a href="/tui-mu" class="svc-card svc-tuimu">
                    <div class="tag-hot-corner">HOT</div>
                    <div class="svc-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-gift"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="svc-title">Túi Mù Gacha</h4>
                    <p class="svc-desc">Chỉ từ 9k/túi. Mở ra Acc Liên Quân VIP, thử thách nhân phẩm.</p>
                    <span class="svc-action">Xé Túi Ngay <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
                </a>

                <a href="/thue-acc" class="svc-card svc-thueacc">
                    <div class="svc-icon-wrap"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="svc-title">Thuê Acc Rẻ</h4>
                    <p class="svc-desc">Trải nghiệm Skin SSS siêu hiếm, nick Thách Đấu từ 5.000đ.</p>
                    <span class="svc-action">Thuê Acc Ngay <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></span>
                </a>

                <a href="/san-acc-1d" class="svc-card svc-san1d">
